    metaDesc: 'Enter your Taiwan invoice carrier ID, pick a background and color, and generate your own Apple Wallet card in seconds.',
    eyebrow: 'Taiwan Invoice Carrier',
    h1a: 'Make your invoice',
    h1b: 'carrier actually cool',
    heroDesc: 'Enter your carrier ID, pick a background, tweak the colors — and get an Apple Wallet card worth showing off.',
